1595F979.Line37.84B74: I will slay her in that cesspit she calls home and open the way to the Heavens. All is as fate decreed: “A spear of Light, piercing Hatred’s heart.”

33FA61D4.Line41.84B74: Rally the troops at the palace. We march on Hell.

6F34E331.Line11.84B74: The time of prophecy has come, Knights. Lilith flees through the gate to Hell.

7BA17FF7.Line35.84B74: Lilith dies by my blade. Prophecy has foretold it.

8F5FAB16.Line25.84B74: But the angels don’t need you.

AF8A72FB.Line39.84B74: You who die in battle today, die Heaven-bound!

C33DEA44.Line29.6D03F: We don’t need the bloody angels either.

E1AD0675.Line33.84B74: You boast of a mere fragment of what this once was. The worldstone, debased in the hands of fools.

F56B3194.Line23.84B74: Ah. The Horadrim. Always chasing after the battles of your betters.
